title: Beau Burchell from Saosin
itunes:title: Beau Burchell from Saosin
description:
This week I have the guitarist from Saosin, Beau Burchell on the show. He's one of my closest friends and we speak frankly about performing live, being an "asshole" and focusing on the creative process above all. It's a very reflective and open conversation about ego, attention and identity. 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
